ReadMe File:

(a) install node js and monogodb:
		1) npm install node
		2) npm install mongodb


(b) npm install 

(c) Start Server : 
		node app.js or nodejs app.js

(d)open browser:
		localhost:3000		  

For Private Chat Type:

/w [name] [message]

name: To whom you want to send private message

To Send File:

Type name of the file and click Send File button

To Send File to specific person

/w [name] [fileName]

Note: For above instructions to work "FILE" should be present in the same directory.


